{"tid":365983,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"那些如果今年發表會破一億views的歌","createTime":"2017-08-19T16:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T07:01:41.000Z","uid":35668,"like":8,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"161a01bfe9ffa6582858b858e69875d4a8156472","tid":365983,"uid":35668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:09:53.000Z","msg":"1. Lady Gaga - Bad Romance (2009)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qrO4YZeyl0I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqrO4YZeyl0I&d=keImneOpu5MvjUlQcgVuOJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=73bd8a20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qrO4YZeyl0I</a><br />\n唔係誇張，女神Gaga今年先出道既話，我諗呢洗腦首歌二億views都有可能<br />\n<br />\n2. Numb - Linkin Park (2007)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kXYiU_JCYtU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkXYiU_JCYtU&d=keImneOpu5MvjUlQcgVuOJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5fb49619\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kXYiU_JCYtU</a><br />\n十年前youtube都未係全世界普及，但呢首歌都可以累積到六百萬views<br />\n<br />\n3. Eminem - Without Me (2002)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YVkUvmDQ3HY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYVkUvmDQ3HY&d=keImneOpu5MvjUlQcgVuOJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=8e2eda6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YVkUvmDQ3HY</a><br />\n首歌2009年upload上youtube，但實際呢首歌年代更加久遠，大家齊來跪拜年少輕狂的rap god<br />\n<br />\n4. Gotye - Somebody That I Used To Know (2011)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8UVNT4wvIGY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8UVNT4wvIGY&d=keImneOpu5MvjUlQcgVuOJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=8b8df444\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8UVNT4wvIGY</a><br />\nGotye我淨係識呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好洗腦又好hit<br />\n<br />\n5. Bruno Mars - Just The Way You Are (2010)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LjhCEhWiKXk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLjhCEhWiKXk&d=keImneOpu5MvjUlQcgVuOJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=aafb09f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LjhCEhWiKXk</a><br />\n輪到火星人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過佢都唔少歌破億啦<br />\n<br />\n6. Rihanna - Umbrella (2007)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CvBfHwUxHIk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCvBfHwUxHIk&d=keImneOpu5MvjUlQcgVuOJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f4005b8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CvBfHwUxHIk</a><br />\n又係有點洗腦的歌，ella ella ella eh eh eh<br />\n<br />\n7. Coldplay - Paradise (2011)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1G4isv_Fylg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1G4isv_Fylg&d=keImneOpu5MvjUlQcgVuOJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d54dbd7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1G4isv_Fylg</a><br />\n<br />\n8. Coldplay - Viva la vida (2008)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dvgZkm1xWPE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdvgZkm1xWPE&d=keImneOpu5MvjUlQcgVuOJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=29943fb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dvgZkm1xWPE</a><br />\nColdplay也有不少耳熟能詳的歌呢<br />\n<br />\n9. Jason Mraz - I'm Yours (2009)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EkHTsc9PU2A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEkHTsc9PU2A&d=keImneOpu5MvjUlQcgVuOJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=346d0204\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EkHTsc9PU2A</a><br />\n可謂八年前的Just the way you are<br />\n<br />\n10. B.o.B - Airplanes ft. Hayley Williams of Paramore (2010)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kn6-c223DUU\" data-sr-url=\"ht